lead_paragraph: Picture captions and credits in some editions on Monday with an article about the absence of a playoff system for college football were reversed in some copies. The top photograph showed Jordan Shipley of Texas and was by Brian Bahr of Getty Images. The bottom photograph showed Alabama’s Julio Jones after a 73-yard touchdown reception and was by Dave Martin of The Associated Press.
